Blocks.Text: Confidentiality Note: This facsimile is intended only for the person or entity to which it is addressed and may contain information their privileged, confidential
or otherwise protected from disclosure Dissemination, distribution or copying of this facsimile or the information herein by anyone other than the intended
recipient, or an employee or agent responsible for delivering the message to the intended recipient, is prohibited. If you have received this facsimile in error,
please notify us immediately by telephone and return the facsimile by mail.
